reviewText: This product turned out to have been used before. The product description says nothing about it being used.

I love this! It is one of the best VCR head cleaners around. Also it is rare and vintage. I use rubbing alcohol and the solution. They equally works fine. I'm a VCR collector, and I use these cleaners when I get a new VCR from the thrift store near me. Again, works really well! Must buy from trusted seller!
It works very well on my VCR.
This is an established product which works well.  It helps extend the life of your tapes and machine. I would buy another one.
